    <p class="text-text-light mb-2 text-sm">The DMSC-042 is originally an Alfa Laval 'Self-Cleaning' disc-stack centrifuge that has been modified specifically for used oil purification. The centrifuge is also augmented with special elastomers to handle acid-treated used oil.</p>
